 such that they remain above all application windows. The following commands must be placed in the Litestep configuration file (step.rc). See the Litestep documentation for help modifying this file.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s2\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel1\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f1\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {LabelAlwaysOnTop
