\par }{\b\f1\fs18 LabelWidth}{\f1\fs18  }{\i\f1\fs18 number}{\f1\fs18 
\par Sets the horizontal size of the label in pixels. If the value is negative then the size is the desktop width minus the given number. Percentages are also supported.
\par 
\par }{\b\f1\fs18 LabelX}{\f1\fs18  }{\i\f1\fs18 number}{\f1\fs18 
