\par 
\par }{\b\f1\fs18 LabelFontColor}{\f1\fs18  }{\i\f1\fs18 color}{\f1\fs18 
\par Sets the color used to display text. If no value is provided then the default depends on whether shadowing is enabled. If it is enabled then the default is white (the shadow color defaults to black), otherwise the default is black.
